                <h1>Elegant Damask Fabric: Timeless Beauty for Home & Fashion</h1>
                <p>Damask is a luxurious fabric known for its intricate patterns and reversible designs, often made from silk, linen, or cotton. Originating from the city of Damascus, this textile adds elegance to home décor and fashion. Its unique weaving technique combines beauty with durability, making it a timeless choice for upholstery and garments.</p>
